{"tid":1028263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最狂電競男女對決 一輸剝衫Bra都除埋","createTime":"2019-02-19T11:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T06:03:17.000Z","uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"842d972b45e87b85e0bf14d39ac72a94e6a0f20f","tid":1028263,"uid":144201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"男女電競賽輸一場除一件<br />\n話說在影片中可以看到當時正在舉行一場《Counter Strike：Global Offensive 》11盤6勝制的賽事，而對戰雙方分別為男子隊的BANANI_BRO以及女子隊BEST OF THE BEST，不過賽事中卻加入一條在正規聯賽中不可能出現的規矩，那就是每輸一回合整隊都要脫下一件衣服！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tLkDrR2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtLkDrR2.jpg&h=d7eb6ae8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93ZMALn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93ZMALn.jpg&h=ada2464c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jURWdw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjURWdw3.jpg&h=d9b837b4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWjgXYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWjgXYJ.jpg&h=11e4b73e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在影片開始時女子隊4比2領先男子隊。不過男子隊之後隨即發力連勝四場，最終以4比6反勝女子隊。至於女子隊最後有否遵守承諾大家看文章最後的的影片就知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KT5caikaZuA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKT5caikaZuA&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=92caa52c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KT5caikaZuA</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人知紋晒身個女仔叫咩名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88948197220dba75902905251a7366453c299b7","tid":1028263,"uid":192581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"又係靠做埋啲痴線嘢宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189e4f5b849d8a4abc1a7b40e1ed2b622209265a","tid":1028263,"uid":144201,"like":0,"di